data.description: This spacious, all-brick gem is a steal of a deal! This all brick beauty with endless potential is nestled on a large lot in the highly sought after, gated community of Neuse Colony. With soaring ceilings, walls of windows and views of nothing but nature, you can't help but feel as if you're on vacation. This home features a two-story family room with a double-sided fireplace, a huge owner's suite with massive WIC, very spacious secondary bedrooms. The basement boasts of a bonus and gameroom, bedroom, full bath and storage. Don't miss out on creating your own masterpiece on this slice of paradise. Home is being sold AS IS. Price reflects upgrades and touch-ups needed. Home has a transferrable termite bond that is transferable at no cost through Neuse Termite & Pest Control. Seller is offering to pay for a one-year First American home warranty for the buyer at closing and seller will pay $5k in closing costs for the buyer.
